title: FM Jilani discusses cooperation with envoys of Finland, Nepal, and Qatar
content:
ISLAMABAD, Nov 23 (APP): Foreign Minister Jalil Abbas Jilani on Thursday held separate meetings with Ambassador Hannu Ripati of Finland, Ambassador Tapas Adhikari of Nepal, and Ambassador Ali bin Mubarak Al-Khater of Qatar.
In the meetings, they discussed enhancing bilateral cooperation in diverse areas.
Ambassador Hannu Ripati of Finland, Ambassador @AdhiTapas of Nepal and Ambassador Ali bin Mubarak Al-Khater of Qatar individually called on FM @JalilJilani today. These meetings focused on enhancing bilateral cooperation in diverse areas. pic.twitter.com/dhWwPuiH6B
— Ministry of Foreign Affairs – Pakistan (@ForeignOfficePk) November 23, 2023
